PrecisAmendment to the SURTAX ON BONELESS BEEF ORDER NO. 2, 1994 which exempts certain cuts of beef, currently unavailable in commercial quantities from domestic production, from the 25% ad valorem surtax established in that Order (eye of round, outside round, outside flat, inside round and sirloin tip).
